    <guid>https://blog.wyi.hk/posts/debian%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%B6%E5%8C%BA/</guid>
    <description><![CDATA[<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 设置时区</span>
